description:
http://www.richievitale.com
An explanation of "4ths & 5ths" intervalic exercises as taught to Richie Vitale by Woody Shaw. 
See my book "A Lyrical Approach to Jazz Improvising" available at: http://www.lulu.com/spotlight/riqiv
title: Woody Shaw "4ths & 5ths" Exercise by Richie Vitale
